OL,3,CWoman with postpartum psychosis
OL,4,Cconsidered taking own life
OL,6,FA Co Tyrone mother who was diagnosed
OL,7,Fwith postpartum psychosis in 2017
OL,8,Fafter the birth of her fourth child
OL,9,Fhas opened up about how she thought if
OL,10,Fshe took her own life it would be
OL,11,Fbetter for her husband and her
OL,12,Fchildren.
OL,14,FTeresa Hawkes from Omagh says a Mother
OL,15,Fand Baby Unit for Northern Ireland is
OL,16,Fcritical to support others who are
OL,17,Fgoing through what she experienced.
