OL,6,FHowever, there are fears because of
OL,7,Ffinancial pressures the new health
OL,8,Fminister won't prioritise finding the
OL,9,Fmoney and it won't go ahead.
OL,11,F"I wanted to drive out into the road
OL,12,Fand wait for a lorry to come. Very
OL,13,Fvery dark moments because I thought if
OL,14,FI was gone life would be better for my
OL,15,Fhusband and children," she told UTV.
OL,17,FThe 46-year-old was admitted to a
OL,18,Fmental health unit in Omagh for two
OL,19,Fweeks. Separated from her new born and
OL,20,Ffamily.
