OL,6,F"That day when she was admitted was
OL,7,Fone of the few times in my life I just
OL,8,Fbroke down after walking out of that
OL,9,Fbuilding. I didn't know what was
OL,10,Fhappening or going on. It was very
OL,11,Ffrightening," her husband Ryan said.
