OL,6,FLiz Morrison from Action on Postpartum
OL,7,FPsychosis NI said: "Our message to
OL,8,F(Health Minister) Mike Nesbitt is the
OL,9,FMother and Baby Unit in Northern
OL,10,FIreland has be a priority. It's grim
OL,11,Fwhen it comes to health funding and we
OL,12,Fknow we are competing with a lot of
OL,13,Fother very valid pressures but women
OL,14,Fare dying."
